data.description: Enjoy majestic Pacific Ocean sunrises and sunsets from nearly every room of this recently remodeled 6 bed, 4 bath home in the heart of Gold Beach.  New features include: composition roof, hardieboard siding, vinyl windows, trim and paint.  The interior boasts new vanities in all bathrooms, tile, laminate, stainless appliances, etc.  Fenced in yard.  Newer deck.   Large carport and room to park an RV/Boat.  1200 sf basement for storage/shop area.  See today before it is gone!
